Subject: AD Sync Incomplete
Description:
Hi,

not all User get Synct to the Adminstrativ Group.
In our AD they are Correctly in the group.

What can i do so that the User gets Synct?
What_We_Know__c:
We are still waiting on the customer to provide us with more details.

2025.04.11 - Customer confirmed that users not being imported are in the same AD groups as the users that are imported.
Next_Steps__c:
We need to know if the users that are not imported into Endpoint Protector are part of the same Groups in the Active Directory.
We asked for a screenshot of the AD Groups showing the users that are imported vs the users that are not imported.

We are waiting on the customer to provide us with the requested details.

2025.04.11 - I have requested a remote session with the customer for Monday 14th April to observer the behavior live.

2025.04.14 - The administrators which were not synchronized and imported was previously deleted from the EPP server, I entered the backend and restores these administrators. The customer performed another synchronization and the administrators were successfully imported and visible on the EPP UI.  Customer confirmed that case can be closed.
